s\"><div class = \"text-block\">Get a fresh well plate, fill up 4 wells with the SDS solution<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":883597,"guid":"482199204F7911EAB1048F32F0507AA6","previous_id":883596,"previous_guid":"4820AEC14F7911EAB1048F32F0507AA6","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"3B77378FF8C84B168C78898D679FADA8","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"931E2058DB7A44DD8042F2870EC79087","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Use the cut-open pipette tip to gently move the slices from EtOH into the SDS solution<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":883599,"guid":"48231FC14F7911EAB1048F32F0507AA6","previous_id":883597,"previous_guid":"482199204F7911EAB1048F32F0507AA6","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"9DE35046EA83405ABA7382DCCEED91F2","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"4C223AC23A18457E9B62338ACBF03375","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Incubate at RT for two hours in the dark with agitation.<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":883600,"guid":"4823E3114F7911EAB1048F32F0507AA6","previous_id":883599,"previous_guid":"48231FC14F7911EAB1048F32F0507AA6","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"D9810C2FBB6D4CDBB781EA96966436E3","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"11B4DCBE98ED4C9F812976994FBCECE3","order_id":1,"ty